Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（由利亚的超技巧）改造男潮吹体质训练
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,身体如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,恢复很慢啊   是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那得好好检查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,发烧了？    有点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,多久了？   一星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都不能运动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟手都成这样了    也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那来检查吧   麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有多烧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好烫啊，那来量一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得快炸了   有喝感冒药么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没有呢    没吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那来量了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来用好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来用好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子不能搓嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,都一星期了，受不了吧？积很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你解放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,手都怎么用？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,右边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让我看一下吗？别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行？   好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你哦，可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来用了   麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,多久了？   一星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,味道一定很刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都可以用奶头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都不会这样么？好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我来用干净哦，可以么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有下流味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头出来吧，来给你舔干净哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都脏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也都用干净哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？    感觉好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,得好好舔干净才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,汗好咸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,味道好赞   害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有多脏呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一星期的量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看么？   害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不舔干净不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好臭呢   对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,得好好搓好好舔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,自己不行呢   是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想用吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如何   好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,自己没办法搓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那要好好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可耻的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔干净么？   可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想更刺激么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,摸了更刺激哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,多摸点，我也会摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都这么硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,老二也要多用点？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:19:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有脏味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想看屁股么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽，等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了   要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还不行哦  要射很多才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,最后才把不好的射出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,射出不好的汁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要全部射出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好热呢  爽么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,手也很爽么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快射了   是么？可以啊，射出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,坏汁要全部射出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,龟头这样子不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,敏感么？因为一星期没用了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢用龟头么？   喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子吗？   真的要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,给我好好用着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快不行了   不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.86,0:23:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那射出来吧    要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要射干净，好可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:24:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好多啊，好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.60,0:24:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,忍着的全部射出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太强了，又要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.86,0:24:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.53,0:24:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能到什么程度？   放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.66,0:25:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一周了呢，那么好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.80,0:25:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快点好比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.93,0:25:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有需要会再来看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.93,0:25:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.60,0:27:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没得射啊？   是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.13,0:27:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要一直插穴吧？    是的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.40,0:27:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.00,0:28:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,享受前要先兴奋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.73,0:28:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴如何？   好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.33,0:29:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴很爽吧？   好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.66,0:29:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.06,0:30:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？有收起来的感觉么？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.66,0:30:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么吸着，只有小穴才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.93,0:30:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.20,0:31:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老二好大
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.60,0:31:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看舌头背面
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.60,0:31:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,给你来诊疗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.86,0:31:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.46,0:32:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老二硬了呢    好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.06,0:32:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好有活力，今天会好好用的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.73,0:33:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,反应真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.40,0:33:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.80,0:33:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽   是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.00,0:33:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋好胀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.46,0:34:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽   这么用很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.93,0:34:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,老二想要被夹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.40,0:34:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的嘴如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.60,0:35:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可以么？会好好吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.93,0:35:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真想直接用
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.19,0:35:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.13,0:35:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不用出来太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.53,0:36:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有硬老二好热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.73,0:36:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这么热会流汗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.13,0:36:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋么？   好兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.13,0:36:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,用出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.46,0:36:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,出来了呢，热老二
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.93,0:36:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,毛都掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.20,0:36:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,老二出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.13,0:37:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,羞汁啊？   以为忍不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.20,0:37:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那什么？   老二汁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.26,0:37:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住就流老二汁么？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.73,0:37:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,龟头都湿了，老二汁好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.66,0:37:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,舔了哦，想要吗？   想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.20,0:37:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老二汁好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.40,0:37:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来诊疗老二了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.80,0:38:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.00,0:38:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爽么？   好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.66,0:38:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,用上很有感觉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.46,0:38:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,用着舒服么？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.00,0:39:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,吃到嘴里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.13,0:39:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来吸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.66,0:39:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.33,0:40:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,来慢慢搓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.80,0:40:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,会给你好好用的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.73,0:40:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴有爽么?   好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.33,0:40:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要看好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.06,0:41:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这么用着舒服么？   好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.53,0:41:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很敏感吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.33,0:41:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这么如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.40,0:41:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,给你用湿湿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.86,0:42:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.93,0:42:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,会用进去了哦，用手和嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.80,0:43:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,想看我的穴么？   想
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.80,0:43:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你看么？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.40,0:43:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不行舔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.26,0:43:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是小穴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.93,0:43:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢么？   最爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.53,0:43:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.20,0:44:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,老二好有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.73,0:44:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,穴汁有流出来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.53,0:44:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？   好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.73,0:44:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.66,0:44:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老二很有感觉么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.53,0:44:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.60,0:45:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再多舔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.60,0:45:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,又软么？很湿吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.26,0:45:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,和以前不同吧？  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.80,0:45:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,应该很明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.13,0:45:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来好好用我的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.33,0:46:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,手指来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.53,0:46:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这里？   对
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.73,0:46:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好好用小穴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.80,0:46:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.80,0:46:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,超紧的   又明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.60,0:46:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴有在动吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.00,0:46:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一根吧   再一根？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.13,0:47:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.33,0:47:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.46,0:47:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有很好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.20,0:47:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.66,0:47:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,多用点
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.60,0:47:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.33,0:47:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是手指好么？   想多感受吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.60,0:48:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想插入么？   想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.53,0:48:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.60,0:48:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.06,0:49:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉么？   好有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.33,0:49:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.00,0:49:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有很紧么？   真紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.73,0:49:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有很爽么？   好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.66,0:50:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？   好赞，好紧好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.20,0:50:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？   好美   是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.20,0:50:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.60,0:50:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.53,0:51:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉真好，进进出出的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.93,0:51:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,得好好用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.86,0:52:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老二要好好用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.40,0:52:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好好感觉我的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.26,0:53:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可以都多用点么？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.33,0:54:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看好小穴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.40,0:54:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.53,0:54:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.33,0:55:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这里头搅起来   真好
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.33,0:55:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.00,0:55:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.93,0:56:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧？   好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.80,0:56:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这么边用着边舔奶头如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.26,0:57:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了？   好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.80,0:58:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好用出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.26,0:58:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爽么？   好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.66,0:58:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想要口水  口水么？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.46,0:59:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.60,0:59:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.40,0:59:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爽么？   好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.40,1:00:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了  就来射吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.26,1:00:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.60,1:00:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还没全射出来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.60,1:00:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.00,1:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再继续射啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.80,1:01:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都射了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.66,1:01:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这精子真好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.33,1:01:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有用好小穴吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.53,1:01:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你来真好   要再来找我哦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.60,1:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法男人潮吹？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.40,1:03:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法？来教你男人的潮吹
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.26,1:03:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要先来用蛋哦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.33,1:03:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很多精子呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.20,1:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,用了蛋也都胀了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.80,1:04:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.93,1:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来用蛋了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.60,1:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.33,1:04:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但有爽么？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.00,1:04:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,紧张么？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.40,1:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张啊，好好爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.40,1:05:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来好好用
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.20,1:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好胀呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.13,1:05:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来让你爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.93,1:05:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋在动，用力了？再来一次
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.40,1:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞，上下动呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.40,1:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.33,1:06:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来舔了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.86,1:06:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来好好用进去
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.53,1:06:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.93,1:07:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有很好吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.00,1:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这里呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.46,1:07:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.73,1:07:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,爽么？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.60,1:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,舔了会如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.86,1:08:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,老二的先用湿呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.00,1:08:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.33,1:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢地搓老二
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.06,1:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要来用龟头
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.60,1:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,会给你好好用的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.13,1:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,两手啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.86,1:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么慢慢地很爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.46,1:09:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.93,1:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这么用着
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.33,1:10:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.46,1:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,用着后面哦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.53,1:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这么转起来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.80,1:11:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,着如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.53,1:11:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很爽
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.66,1:11:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.66,1:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这么摩很爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.93,1:11:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,激烈一点哦，很爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.66,1:12:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我变的好躁了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.00,1:12:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可以用奶么？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.13,1:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一般搓着用奶头哦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.06,1:12:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,知道奶头用上了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.46,1:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.86,1:12:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,多用点
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.40,1:13:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,忍很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.46,1:13:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但还不行
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.33,1:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够哦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.26,1:13:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,多看点你下流的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.20,1:13:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,敏感是吧，爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.66,1:14:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞么？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.13,1:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞也无妨啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.93,1:14:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要多害羞点
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.80,1:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.40,1:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.53,1:17:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,继续哦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.53,1:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,搓得这么爽么？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.53,1:17:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真开心
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.73,1:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,男人的潮吹是在射之后
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.93,1:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到时就会喷出来
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.26,1:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有知道了么？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.06,1:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是尿道口哦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.60,1:18:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了呢，不会痛吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.73,1:18:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,用到尿道了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.93,1:18:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这里么？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.80,1:19:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是咸味
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.46,1:19:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那来用了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.66,1:19:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,用着蛋，也搓着老二哦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.20,1:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,搓着很爽吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.60,1:20:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快要射了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.60,1:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.86,1:20:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就像女人一样喷出来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.20,1:20:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,会让你像女人一样的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.26,1:20:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,像女人一样喷吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.73,1:21:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要再多一点么？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.80,1:21:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都射了么？还没么？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.93,1:22:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有好么？还是没有？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.73,1:22:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次就喷这么多
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.20,1:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真像女人的身体
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.86,1:22:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,再来就自己试试吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.53,1:24:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要来用
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.66,1:24:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不想不用吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.40,1:24:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.40,1:24:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,往后3年不搞都行  想啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.46,1:25:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这么想么？   想搞啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.20,1:25:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还没哦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.93,1:25:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.26,1:25:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还要有顺序的   好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.20,1:25:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,料好大啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.66,1:25:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,都流汗了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.40,1:26:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,奶都这么了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.06,1:26:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还没哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.60,1:26:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你好好用的，可以么？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.60,1:26:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.80,1:26:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,想用啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.53,1:26:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.00,1:27:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怜，看来都没什么用呢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.33,1:27:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想要KISS？   嘴   嘴就好？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.66,1:28:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要冷静了么？   再来
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.86,1:28:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有好么？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.73,1:28:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看来好爽呢
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.13,1:29:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真理看好么？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.00,1:29:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可以用哦，要慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.13,1:30:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,另一边也来
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.86,1:30:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想看吧？   想啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.80,1:30:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来好好摸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.86,1:30:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好好揉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.20,1:30:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可以好好用着哦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.60,1:30:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多汗呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.60,1:31:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.66,1:31:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,爽么？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.66,1:31:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这么美味么？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.53,1:31:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有好么？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.33,1:31:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,老二都兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.06,1:31:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这么用吗？   喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.06,1:31:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真好的老二
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.00,1:32:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,想插啊   还不行插哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.93,1:32:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想插啊   想啊？不行
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.60,1:32:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有顺序的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.26,1:32:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.80,1:32:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真羞耻的样子
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.13,1:33:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,得好好搓吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.93,1:33:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不够么？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.06,1:33:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这羞耻的样子变的更湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.53,1:34:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋很爽么？   好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.60,1:34:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,老二打湿哦
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.06,1:34:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋和老二都这样了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.00,1:34:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.66,1:34:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬的老二
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.53,1:35:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.73,1:35:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,想插啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.26,1:35:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想插么？    想
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.26,1:35:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真没办法，就来插吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.26,1:35:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.06,1:36:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想插么？    想
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.60,1:36:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这么想插啊？就给你插哦
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.53,1:36:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了哦   好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.93,1:36:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是你最爱的小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.20,1:36:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴？   对
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.13,1:37:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.53,1:37:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有很好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.60,1:38:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃么？   好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.26,1:38:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.86,1:38:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.33,1:38:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再来   小穴好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.86,1:38:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.66,1:39:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个是这里
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.53,1:39:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不能马上插   想插啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.53,1:39:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想插   可以
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.93,1:40:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽   多插一点
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.80,1:40:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,顶到里头呢   好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.26,1:40:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽么？   真好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.13,1:41:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,多插一点
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.20,1:42:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.66,1:43:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,老二好湿，想再插么？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.60,1:43:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想插穴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.46,1:43:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽   从后面好好插哦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.46,1:43:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有好吧？    好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.73,1:43:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽   再来
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.93,1:44:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一直看到呢   好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.13,1:45:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.66,1:45:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还不行射哦
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.20,1:45:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢屁股么？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.20,1:45:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,想多插点么？    想
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.46,1:45:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,插很好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.73,1:45:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.60,1:46:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有好吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.40,1:46:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽么？   好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.73,1:47:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在让小穴多点感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.33,1:47:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.00,1:47:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,老二想如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.66,1:48:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想射么？   想啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.66,1:48:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.93,1:48:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有好么？   小穴真好
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.86,1:48:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这么好么？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.00,1:49:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽    是么？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.46,1:49:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.26,1:50:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,想射   还不行哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.13,1:50:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等等射出来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.20,1:50:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.60,1:51:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再来   再来？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.46,1:51:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喷出来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.60,1:51:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了   不行停哦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.86,1:51:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.33,1:52:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.53,1:52:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,射这么多一定爽嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.06,1:52:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看来可以了么
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.86,1:52:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真没办法呢   可以舔么？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.46,1:53:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这么会再射么？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.46,1:53:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.73,1:54:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,爽么？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.66,1:54:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想看下流精啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.46,1:54:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.80,1:54:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的手射出来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.40,1:54:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想再看看很多的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.20,1:54:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,再来么？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.53,1:55:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.20,1:55:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？  还有吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.73,1:56:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还会射么？不够么？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.06,1:56:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还一直射呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.26,1:56:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很努力呢，好孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.80,1:57:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看来没问题了，暂时不用也可以
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.00,1:57:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,爽么
